window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>With Tarnil free, Blue and his allies consolidate and recover from the mage-king's depredations. As he establishes himself firmly at home, he starts reaching out to the world that he is now a part of. There is a lot of work to be done to prevent further war, or worse.</p> <p>Book two of the Blue Core series. This story contains occasional scenes of explicit consensual sex.</p>"; 
